description: Overview of RDS instances in a region
title: RDS Overview

Account.name: Account
Account.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_account_id') as cloud_account_id
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE 
    metric_name like 'aws_RDS_CPUUtilization_sum'
GROUP BY cloud_account_id

Region.name: Region
Region.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_region') as cloud_region
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE 
    metric_name like 'aws_RDS_CPUUtilization_sum'
    and JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_account_id') IN {{.Account}}
GROUP BY cloud_region

widgets.description:
The amount of available random access memory.

For MariaDB, MySQL, Oracle, and PostgreSQL DB instances, this metric reports the value of the MemAvailable field of /proc/meminfo.
widgets.title: Free Memory
